The paper deals with face recognition, which is a common application of computer vision (cs.CV) and pattern recognition (cs.LG) methods. The proposed algorithm involves learning subspaces, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates the algorithm on benchmark face image databases, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
